title: Federal Court finds Lyoness scheme not pyramid (Australian Competition and Consumer Commission)
text: ( Source : Australian Competition and Consumer Commission ) The Federal Court has found that a loyalty program operated by Lyoness Australia Pty Ltd does not contravene the pyramid and referral selling provisions of the Australian Consumer Law
